      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! This car has been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape\u2014it's perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I've kept up with the basics, and she runs like a charm. It\u2019s got a lot of heart left, and I\u2019d love to see it go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have. Come check it out and take her for a spin!",
