    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies. This example has been properly sorted with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing precision. Power is managed through a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The suspension geometry remains tight with updated bushings, offering the communicative feedback these chassis are known for. While the aesthetics show honest patina consistent with a well-loved driver, the powertrain delivers peak torque and a crisp 8,000 RPM redline without hesitation.",
