      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers the perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium leather upholstery is soft and free of tears, though there is light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every button, switch, and digital display functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a strict preventative maintenance schedule, including a recent fluid service and a fresh set of high-performance tires. The engine pulls smoothly, the transmission shifts are crisp, and the suspension remains taut and quiet. This is a smoke-free, garage-kept example that represents an excellent opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable, high-quality ride without the showroom price tag.",
